data.description: ALL APPLIANCES TO REMAIN INCLUDING REFRIGERATOR, WASHER/DRYER AND GUEST BEDROOM FURNITURE.  Welcome Home to this adorable low maintenance home just off Oneal Lane.  The footprint of this home engages the whole family together with the openness of the family room, dining room and kitchen.  Becoming a homeowner, you will love preparing dinner for the family or entertaining on the custom island with the breakfast bar.  Master bedroom offers walk in closet, large custom vanity with oil bronze hardware fixtures.  Located in the hallway are walk in utility room and linen closet. Relax on the cozy patio just off the living area.  Call today for your private tour.
